page_content: The page provides information on tax rates for withholding tax in the Canton of Schwyz for the year 2020.
The page offers information on eTax.SZ, a software for filing tax returns online and as a desktop application.
The page provides information and guidelines on fruit cultivation and plant protection in the Canton of Schwyz.
The page provides information on judicial internships offered by the Administrative Court of the Canton of Schwyz.
The page outlines the building permit process for industrial and non-industrial businesses in the Canton of Schwyz.
The page details the regulations for Sunday sales and public holidays in the Canton of Schwyz.
The page provides information on commercial supervision, including regulations on passive smoking, gambling, and consumer credit in the Canton of Schwyz.
